<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>量化终端 · 旗舰版</title>
    <style>
        /* 1. 还原 27444 的深墨绿背景与全局网格 */
        body { 
            background: #0d120f; color: #fff; font-family: sans-serif; margin: 0; 
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(45, 62, 52, 0.3) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(45, 62, 52, 0.3) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 25px 25px;
        }

        /* 2. 内陷式卡片设计 */
        .panel { 
            background: #1a231e; margin: 10px 15px; padding: 20px; border-radius: 25px; 
            border: 1px solid #2d3e34; box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); text-align: center;
        }
        .bal-val { font-size: 55px; color: #ff5a5a; font-weight: bold; }
        .bet-info { color: #f1c40f; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px; }

        /* 3. 雷达网格转盘 */
        .wheel-area { flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative; }
        #wheel { 
            width: 320px; height: 320px; border-radius: 50%; border: 12px solid #233129;
            /* 还原图 27444 的绿色雷达网格底纹 */
            background: #1a231e;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#2d3e34 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(#2d3e34 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #2d3e34 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 100% 100%, 20px 20px, 20px 20px;
            position: relative; box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
        }
        #wheel::after { content: "准备"; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); width: 85px; height: 85px; background: #1a231e; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #ff5a5a; font-weight: bold; font-size: 22px; border: 4px solid #233129; }
        
        .animal-node { position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding-top: 25px; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .animal-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        .animal-name { font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; color: #8aa095; }

        /* 4. 底部红色操作面板 */
        .ctrl-panel { background: #3d0e0e; padding: 20px; border-radius: 30px 30px 0 0; border-top: 2px solid #631b1b; }
        .main-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .side-btn { width: 55px; height: 55px; background: #261111; border-radius: 15px; color: #ff5a5a; font-size: 30px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 1px solid #631b1b; }
        .btn-play { background: #cc2929; color: #fff; padding: 18px 70px; border-radius: 40px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; border: none; box-shadow: 0 6px 0 #801a1a; }
        
        .status-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-around; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .status-pill { background: #261111; padding: 8px 25px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #8aa095; border: 1px solid #4a1414; }
        .nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-around; padding: 15px 0; background: #000; font-size: 11px; color: #8aa095; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div style="text-align:center; padding:10px; color:#f1c40f; font-size:12px;">⚡ 量化终端 · 公平游戏 ⚡</div>

    <div class="panel">
        <div style="color:#8aa095; font-size:13px;">💰 可用余额 (USDT)</div>
        <div class="bal-val">1000.00</div> <div class="bet-info">🔥 单注额度: 10.0</div>
    </div>

    <div class="wheel-area">
        <div style="position:absolute; top:5%; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:0; height:0; border-left:20px solid transparent; border-right:20px solid transparent; border-top:30px solid #ff0000; z-index:10;"></div>
        <div id="wheel">
            <div class="animal-node" style="transform:rotate(0deg)"><span class="animal-icon">🐺</span><span class="animal-name">孤狼</span></div>
            <div class="animal-node" style="transform:rotate(45deg)"><span class="animal-icon">🦢</span><span class="animal-name" style="transform:rotate(-45deg)">仙鹤</span></div>
            <div class="animal-node" style="transform:rotate(90deg)"><span class="animal-icon">🐢</span><span class="animal-name" style="transform:rotate(-90deg)">玄武</span></div>
            <div class="animal-node" style="transform:rotate(135deg)"><span class="animal-icon">🦅</span><span class="animal-name" style="transform:rotate(-135deg)">大鹏</span></div>
            <div class="animal-node" style="transform:rotate(180deg)"><span class="animal-icon">🐯</span><span class="animal-name" style="transform:rotate(-180deg)">猛虎</span></div>
            <div class="animal-node" style="transform:rotate(225deg)"><span class="animal-icon">🦄</span><span class="animal-name" style="transform:rotate(-225deg)">麒麟</span></div>
            <div class="animal-node" style="transform:rotate(270deg)"><span class="animal-icon">🐲</span><span class="animal-name" style="transform:rotate(-270deg)">神龙</span></div>
            <div class="animal-node" style="transform:rotate(315deg)"><span class="animal-icon">🔥</span><span class="animal-name" style="transform:rotate(-315deg)">凤凰</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ctrl-panel">
        <div class="main-row">
            <div class="side-btn">−</div>
            <button class="btn-play" onclick="alert('执行中...')">▶ 执行抽取</button>
            <div class="side-btn">+</div>
        </div>
        <div class="status-row">
            <div class="status-pill">🤖 自动模式：关</div>
            <div class="status-pill">⚡ 变速：1X</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nav">
        <span>📈 行情</span><span>💹 资产中心</span><span>📜 历史记录</span><span style="color:#fff">🎚️ 量化终端</span>
    </div>

</body>
</html>